15:11.130 --> 15:12.000
after school.

15:13.110 --> 15:13.710
Got it.

15:26.260 --> 15:26.940
I'm here to pay for the noodle snack

15:26.960 --> 15:27.960
I took this morning.

15:29.620 --> 15:30.020
Huh?

15:30.460 --> 15:31.980
A girl has already paid for it.

15:32.600 --> 15:33.840
She said

15:33.920 --> 15:34.790
you won first place today.

15:35.030 --> 15:35.630
It's on her.

15:40.130 --> 15:41.290
Then I'll buy something else.

16:01.730 --> 16:02.920
W-who left this?

16:07.090 --> 16:07.800
I did.

16:10.730 --> 16:12.190
Chen asked me to put it here.

16:12.500 --> 16:14.380
He said you asked him to buy it for you.

16:17.680 --> 16:18.680
Please thank him for me.

16:19.490 --> 16:19.810
What?

16:19.830 --> 16:21.390
He's just in class 7 next door.

16:21.500 --> 16:22.380
You can thank him yourself.

16:24.220 --> 16:24.650
Okay, fine.

16:24.680 --> 16:26.000
I'll go.

16:32.820 --> 16:33.300
Chen.

16:33.680 --> 16:34.870
Gui Xiao says thank you.

16:37.930 --> 16:38.530
